with us. but if I do.

777
00:40:30.137 --> 00:40:32.472
you're going to jail.
and they'll kill you inside.

778
00:40:34.599 --> 00:40:35.976
And then they'll come
for your family.

779
00:40:36.059 --> 00:40:37.602
and you know
what they'll do to them.

780
00:40:37.686 --> 00:40:39.729
It's your call.

781
00:40:43.775 --> 00:40:45.569
Hail Mary...

782
00:40:45.652 --> 00:40:47.404
full of grace.

783
00:40:47.487 --> 00:40:49.906
the Lord is with thee.
blessed are thou...

784
00:40:49.990 --> 00:40:51.992
Take a deep breath.

785
00:41:32.282 --> 00:41:35.952
You do not mess
with the Special Investigators.

786
00:41:36.036 --> 00:41:38.371
You do not mess

787
00:41:38.455 --> 00:41:41.082
with the Special Investigators.

788
00:41:46.838 --> 00:41:48.840
Try these.

789
00:42:01.937 --> 00:42:03.813
What now?

790
00:42:03.897 --> 00:42:06.316
If Kliner forced
that cop to kill us.

791
00:42:06.399 --> 00:42:08.818
odds are he hired
the Viking. too.

792
00:42:08.902 --> 00:42:11.279
Finlay's breaking
into Kliner's office tonight.

793
00:42:11.363 --> 00:42:13.031
Maybe when he flips
over that rock.

794
00:42:13.114 --> 00:42:14.783
something important
will scurry out.

795
00:42:14.866 --> 00:42:16.534
I'm gonna head back to Margrave.

796
00:42:25.585 --> 00:42:27.504
You got to be shittin' me.

797
00:42:31.466 --> 00:42:34.177
This turned into more
than you bargained for

798
00:42:34.261 --> 00:42:36.096
when you agreed to help.

799
00:42:36.179 --> 00:42:38.473
Do me a favor and walk away.

800
00:42:38.556 --> 00:42:40.392
From the guys who killed your
brother and tried to kill us?

801
00:42:40.475 --> 00:42:42.018
Right.

802
00:42:42.102 --> 00:42:43.436
It's not a request.

803
00:42:43.520 --> 00:42:45.480
And you're not
my commanding officer anymore.

804
00:42:46.690 --> 00:42:48.900
I'm going back to Memphis.

805
00:42:48.984 --> 00:42:50.694
See what I can find out
about The Viking.

806
00:42:50.777 --> 00:42:52.946
I'll call you when I know more.

807
00:42:57.742 --> 00:42:59.619
Be safe. boss.

808
00:42:59.703 --> 00:43:02.247
You. too.

809
00:45:46.911 --> 00:45:49.539
Guess you're not pulling
all the strings. huh. Kliner?
